"name": "母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能聽出來，祥子一直都很努力，即使在外辛苦工作，也從來沒有忘記練琴哦。", "name": "母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺祥子在外面經歷了很多呢……", "name": "母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然很不想打擾你們練琴，但飯已經煮好囉？", "name": "父親"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g5_sakikodininghall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——好吃！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？我的手藝進步了吧？", "name": "父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你都不知道……他逼我試吃了多少次，才有現在這個味道。", "name": "母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃吃看這盤沙拉，味道怎麼樣？", "name": "父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，很好吃！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了能讓祥子喜歡，我微調了好幾次口味哦！還不錯吧。", "name": "父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有很多祥子也會喜歡的菜哦！", "name": "父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 